:54.000Z","msg":"同埋有睇過831太子藍絲同黑衫後生仔嘈果陣既片<br />\n<br />\n藍絲都好易分到黑衫而做出對抗<br />\n換平民裝，係可以騎劫到藍絲<br />\n只係剩返平民，老年，中年，後生之分<br />\n<br />\n無人知道邊個打邊個，諗緊d咩"},{"pid":"e1b08e90bf1c8a20be22250d18fe7e86683c52f1","tid":1552253,"uid":211933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c7c0beb5f5cbc52f629e0b342b3016780c64a5ab","tid":1552253,"uid":21275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4b26f54578081ea5f16bad17ae849f32e5403ae7","tid":1552253,"uid":211933,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e4b97509f1197e9d018c293682c8e73d54aebf7c","tid":1552253,"uid":21275,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T10:07:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T10:19:56.000Z","msg":"其實香港人會抗爭既動員能力<br />\n唔會質疑&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n我係諗緊透明如水，be water果下<br />\n大型示威運動，如果受警狗衝刺既打人捉人既時候<br />\n面對既唔係黑衫而係平民<br />\n<br />\n做成既畫面就會係警察打平民<br />\n<br />\n而警狗一走神無左目標，就會無色認<br />\n<br />\n又或者係<br />\n<br />\n831果次，警狗捉人<br />\n示威者免左換裝果下既時間，同考慮換裝既地點<br />\n<br />\n呢d都會比鬼，同埋藍絲輕易影到同篤灰"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T10:22:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T10:28:32.000Z","msg":"呢個講法係要認真考慮&hellip;<br />\n我認同cid著便裝係我地既風險&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n但係宜加出得尼發夢既人，其實都好嚴守到<br />\n不影相不拍攝大頭既戒律<br />\n<br />\n如果見到有可疑人影野，一樣可以捉"},{"pid":"e58118a06b281d2c4c1b6f98db038ae89da1f626","tid":1552253,"uid":211933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T10:32:43.000Z","msg":"推5/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7535ab875b4c369c14ddb54a45a35425bf11c6a8","tid":1552253,"uid":211933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T10:33:09.000Z","msg":"推4/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\